---
<section class="anthem">
  <div class="container">
    <div>
      <div class="label">Built by operators · For operators</div>
      <h2>
        Real data,<br />
        <span class="italic">for real use,</span><br />
        in real time.
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p>
        The CLA wasn't built by a research firm. It was built in the back office of a multi-unit operation,
        used for each market entry and every six months to make actual pricing decisions. Refined for three
        years before it was offered to other operators.
      </p>
      <p>
        Source-cited. Triple-verified. Delivered in 14 days, twice a year. The same tool we use ourselves.
      </p>
      <a href="/method" class="link-uc">Read the method<span class="arrow">›</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .anthem {
    background: var(--dark); color: #fff;
    padding: var(--section) 2rem;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .anthem::before {
    content: ""; position: absolute; top: 0; bottom: 0; left: 50%; width: 1px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); transform: translateX(-50%);
  }
  .container {
    max-width: var(--max); margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr; gap: 5rem; align-items: center;
    position: relative;
  }
  .label {
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--tan-soft); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-left: 1rem; border-left: 2px solid var(--periwinkle);
  }
  h2 {
    font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: #fff; max-width: 12em;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 72;
  }
  h2 .italic { font-style: italic; color: var(--tan-soft); font-weight: 400; }
  .sub-anthem {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--periwinkle);
  }
  p {
    font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 300; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-variation-settings: "opsz" 20;
  }
  .link-uc { color: #fff; border-color: var(--periwinkle); }
  .link-uc:hover { color: var(--periwinkle); }
</style>
